Application

Class LissBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • Application.LissBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LissListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class LissBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements LissListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of LissListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
